Privacy Policy

App Name: Phasmophobia Companion
Developer: Leviathan IX
Last Updated: February 2026

Phasmophobia Companion is an unofficial companion app for the game Phasmophobia. It is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by Kinetic Games.

1) What data we collect

We collect limited technical and usage data to help the app run better:

App activity (analytics)

Examples: screens viewed, buttons tapped, feature usage

Device and identifiers

Examples: device model, operating system version, anonymous device identifiers

Crash logs (diagnostics)

Examples: crash reports, performance data, diagnostic information

2) What we do not collect

We do not collect:

Names

Email addresses

Phone numbers

Precise location

Approximate location

Advertising identifiers

Payment information

User account data

We do not show ads.

3) How we use data

We use the collected data only to:

Maintain and improve app functionality

Monitor stability and performance

Understand general feature usage trends

We do not use data for advertising or marketing.

4) Sharing of data

We do not sell user data.

We do not share user data with third parties for advertising or marketing.

5) Data security

Data sent through Google Play Services and Firebase is encrypted in transit using standard security protocols.

6) Data retention and deletion

The app does not require accounts and does not store personal user data.
You can uninstall the app at any time to stop future data collection from your device.

7) Contact

If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact the developer at: official.leviathan.ix@gmail.com
